    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "The problem here is that with prompt-toolkit, terminal settings are not restored. Would it be an option to add this to the exit function? Otherwise terminal is left with disabled echo and so on.\n\nAlternatively, document a way to revert this keybinding so that Ctrl-\\ sends SIGQUIT (which is what the terminal does in Linux by default); then terminal settings can be restored in the signal handler.\n"
