    "body": "Solved. The problem was here. I forgot my code overrides sys.exit to avoid shutdown issues in external lib - it calls a c++ routine doing some cleanup and then calling exit(1), which explains why the python cleanup restoring terminal was never called. The \"Exit message:\" is also from my code. Apologies and thanks for helping. Keep up the great work on IPython!\n"
